杰斐逊星舰鼓手约翰·巴巴塔去世，享年 79 岁https://www.nme.com/news/music/jefferson-starship-drummer-john-barbata-has-died-age-79-3756280?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=jefferson-starship-drummer-john-barbata-已去世，年龄 79 岁Surej SinghWed, 15 May 2024 02:58:21 +0000 Music NewsNews..Rock https://www.nme.com/?p=3756280 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/john-barbata@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/john-barbata@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/john-barbata@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/john-barbata@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/john-barbata@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/john-barbata@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/john-barbata@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>巴巴塔还曾为 Jefferson Airplane、The Turtles 和 Crosby、Stills、Nash &amp; Young 等球队效力</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jefferson-starship-drummer-john-barbata-has-died-age-79-3756280">杰斐逊星舰后鼓手约翰·巴巴塔去世，享年 79 岁，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/john-barbata@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/john-barbata@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/john-barbata@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/john-barbata@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/john-barbata@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/john-barbata@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/john-barbata@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Jefferson Starship 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jefferson-airplane">Jefferson Airplane</a>等乐队的美国资深鼓手约翰·巴巴塔 (John Barbata) 去世，享年 79 岁。</p><p>周一晚上，杰斐逊星舰的官方 Facebook 页面宣布了这一消息，页面上写道：“我们对伟大的杰斐逊星舰最初的鼓手约翰·巴巴塔去世的消息感到悲痛。我们的思念来自他的家人、朋友和粉丝。安静地摇滚吧，约翰尼！” </p><div id="fb-root"></div><p><script async="1" defer="1" crossorigin="anonymous" src="https://connect.facebook.net/en_US/sdk.js#xfbml=1&amp;version=v19.0" nonce="KDrU6KIr"></script></p><div class="fb-post" data-href="https://www.facebook.com/officialjeffersonstarship/posts/pfbid0FgsKbjNs9g7kFEibjdRpabcs8kbqT5ZPBFT25F7nakFXGZncKRr78hstkK7j8XVkl" data-width="696"><blockquote cite="https://graph.facebook.com/100044261327794/posts/1012514613567240/" class="fb-xfbml-parse-ignore"><p>得知杰斐逊星舰最初的鼓手、伟大的约翰·巴巴塔去世的消息，我们深感悲痛。我们向他的家人、朋友和粉丝表示哀悼。安静地摇滚吧，约翰尼！</p><p>发布者： <a href="https://www.facebook.com/officialjeffersonstarship">Jefferson Starship</a>于<a href="https://graph.facebook.com/100044261327794/posts/1012514613567240/">2024 年 5 月 13 日星期一</a></p></blockquote></div><p>据<a href="https://bestclassicbands.com/john-barbata-drummer-dead-obituary-5-11-24/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Best Classic Bands</em></a>报道，Barbata 于 5 月 8 日去世。死因尚未公布。</p><p>除了在 Jefferson Starship 中打鼓之外，Barbata 还因与 Jefferson Airplane、Crosby、Stills、Nash &amp; Young、The Turtles、The Sentinels 和其他各种乐队的合作而闻名。</p><p>在冲浪摇滚乐队 The Sentinels 工作一段时间后，约翰·巴尔巴塔 (John Barbata) 于 1966 年加入 The Turtles，并与他们一起在主流音乐界取得了成功。他为 1967 年的热门单曲“Happy Together”以及 60 年代末的热门单曲“Elenore”和“You Showed Me”录制了鼓。 </p><figure id="attachment_3756285" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3756285" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3756285" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/barbata-1978@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/barbata-1978@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/barbata-1978@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/barbata-1978@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/barbata-1978@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/barbata-1978@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/barbata-1978@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3756285" class="wp-caption-text"> 1978 年 9 月，约翰·巴巴塔 (John Barbata) 与美国摇滚乐队 Jefferson Starship 一起在美国纽约演出。（摄影：Michael Putland/Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p> 1969 年，Barbata 离开 The Turtles，加入<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/crosby-stills-and-nash">Crosby、Stills、Nash &amp; Young</a>进行了一系列巡演，并出现在乐队 1974 年的现场专辑《4 Way Street》中。他将继续与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-crosby">大卫·克罗斯比</a>、史蒂芬·斯蒂尔斯、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/graham-nash">格雷厄姆·纳什</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/neil-young">尼尔·杨</a>一起在团体和个人项目的各种迭代中录制唱片。</p><div class="enhancement" data-click="enhancement" data-align-center=""></div><p>在接下来的几年里，巴巴塔与琳达·朗斯塔特、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joni-mitchell">乔尼·米切尔</a>、莱昂·拉塞尔和埃弗利兄弟等众多艺术家一起录制唱片并巡回演出。根据他的传记，他拒绝了为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elvis-presley">埃尔维斯·普雷斯利</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eagles">老鹰乐队</a>担任鼓手的<a href="https://www.phoenixnewtimes.com/music/why-johny-barbata-chose-to-drum-for-csnandy-instead-of-the-eagles-6613586" target="_blank" rel="noopener">邀请</a>。</p><p>随后，Barbata 与 Jefferson Airplane 一起制作了他们的最后一张录音室专辑，即 1972 年的“Long John Silver”。他还在 1973 年的现场唱片“Thirty Seconds over Winterland”中担任鼓手。 Jefferson Airplane 随后更名为 Jefferson Starship，Barbata 继续与 Grace Slick、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jefferson-airplane-3-1188882">Paul Katner</a>等人一起在 1974 年至 1979 年间发行了几张专辑。 </p><figure id="attachment_3756286" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3756286" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3756286" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/john-barbata-1978@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/john-barbata-1978@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/john-barbata-1978@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/john-barbata-1978@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/john-barbata-1978@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/john-barbata-1978@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/john-barbata-1978@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3756286" class="wp-caption-text"> 1978 年 9 月，约翰·巴巴塔 (John Barbata) 与美国摇滚乐队 Jefferson Starship 一起在美国纽约演出。（摄影：Michael Putland/Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>在他去世的消息传出后，杰斐逊飞机在社交媒体上写道：“安息吧，约翰·巴巴塔，杰斐逊飞机和杰斐逊星舰的传奇鼓手。”</p><p> “约翰以其非凡的才华而闻名，他与 The Turtles、Crosby、Stills、Nash &amp; Young、Jefferson Airplane 和 Jefferson Starship 等乐队一起演奏，在音乐界留下了自己的印记。早在 72 年，CS​​N&amp;Y 中断期间，大卫·克罗斯比 (David Crosby) 向飞机公司介绍了约翰，飞机公司立即雇用了约翰。您可以在乐队的最后一张录音室专辑“LONG JOHN SILVER”以及现场专辑“THIRTY SECONDS OVER WINTERLAND”中听到约翰的击鼓技巧。 </p><div id="fb-root"></div><p><script async="1" defer="1" crossorigin="anonymous" src="https://connect.facebook.net/en_US/sdk.js#xfbml=1&amp;version=v19.0" nonce="BdIyxc89"></script></p><div class="fb-post" data-href="https://www.facebook.com/JeffersonAirplaneOfficial/posts/pfbid021dHZLz7nen7pMS8KCWjRhVroSngutoeJZxZ1hXKT84WrXqmunosTQxpjKbNH8bD7l" data-width="696"><blockquote cite="https://graph.facebook.com/100044560710777/posts/991954712299877/" class="fb-xfbml-parse-ignore"><p>安息吧，约翰·巴巴塔，杰斐逊飞机和杰斐逊星舰的传奇鼓手<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f54a.png" alt="🕊" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />因他的…</p><p>发布者：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/JeffersonAirplaneOfficial">杰斐逊飞机</a>于<a href="https://graph.facebook.com/100044560710777/posts/991954712299877/">2024 年 5 月 13 日星期一</a></p></blockquote></div><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jefferson-starship-drummer-john-barbata-has-died-age-79-3756280">杰斐逊星舰后鼓手约翰·巴巴塔去世，享年 79 岁，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
